Fy_oscla is a little Map Created by Me (Skope).

It's only made to train skill, and to have fun.
It's playing in a little place of a city, with 2 houses, and some more.

Bugs i know:
 
-you can't see through the glasses of the 2 houses
-some details/props are a little bit dark

Please rate and comment this Map. Critik is welcome.

I hope you enjoy my little fy map.
